                        "content": "Standard dry-cleaning methods are a gamble with your creation. Harsh chemicals can dissolve adhesives, weaken foam structures, strip paint from props, and distort delicate hand-stitched details. Our process was developed with cosplayers in mind: we use cold-water hand techniques, costume-safe spot treatments, and meticulous inspection for hidden wear. Every zipper, snap, and piece of armor is treated with the respect it deserves—because we know your costume isn’t just clothing, it’s your craft.",
                        "align": "left"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "“We don’t clean costumes—we preserve artistry.”",
                        "align": "center"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "blocks": [
                      {
                        "type": "image",
                        "src": "before-after.jpg",
                        "alt": "Before and after of a cleaned costume"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
